### AGI Model Factory API Tests
### Usage: cd api-tests && httpyac run *.http
### Or:   httpyac api-tests/health.http

###############################
### Health & Status
###############################

### Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/health

### DB Ping
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/db/ping

### Dashboard Summary
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/dashboard/summary

###############################
### Evaluations
###############################

### List Evaluations
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/evaluations?limit=10

### Get Single Evaluation
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/evaluations/1f31dfe7-51a9-4048-b53d-642407626ee3

### Evaluation Lineage
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/evaluations/1f31dfe7-51a9-4048-b53d-642407626ee3/lineage

### Evaluation Metrics
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/evaluations/1f31dfe7-51a9-4048-b53d-642407626ee3/metrics

